kw.name: Open Browser
kw.doc: Opens a new browser instance to the optional ``url``.

kw.name: Maximize Browser Window
kw.doc: Maximizes current browser window.

kw.name: Dado que estou na tela Cadastrar Perfil
Go To
kw.doc: Navigates the current browser window to the provided ``url``.

kw.name: Wait Until Page Contains
kw.doc: Waits until ``text`` appears on the current page.

kw.name: Quando preencho o campo "Nome Completo" com @Nome_Completo
Input Text
kw.doc: Types the given ``text`` into the text field identified by ``locator``.

kw.name: E preencho o campo "Data Nascimento" com @Data_Nascimento
Input Text
kw.doc: Types the given ``text`` into the text field identified by ``locator``.

kw.name: E forneço uma @Impressao_Digital válida no campo “Impressão Digital”
Click Element
kw.doc: Click the element identified by ``locator``.

kw.name: Wait Until Element Is Visible
kw.doc: Waits until the element ``locator`` is visible.

kw.name: E realizo o upload de uma imagem com a opção @Escolher_Arquivo no campo "Escolher Arquivo"
Choose File
kw.doc: Inputs the ``file_path`` into the file input field ``locator``.

kw.name: E seleciono a opção @Francês no dropdown de sugestões do campo "Preferência de Idioma"
Select From List By Value
kw.msg: Selecting options from selection list 'id=idioma' by value fr.
kw.doc: Selects options from selection list ``locator`` by ``values``.

kw.name: E seleciono a opção @Alto no dropdown de sugestões do campo "Nível de Privacidade"
Select From List By Value
kw.msg: Selecting options from selection list 'id=privacidade' by value alto.
kw.doc: Selects options from selection list ``locator`` by ``values``.

kw.name: E seleciono a checkbox no campo "Aceito a coleta de dados para análise personalizada"
Select Checkbox
kw.doc: Selects the checkbox identified by ``locator``.

kw.name: Set Window Size
kw.doc: Sets current windows size to given ``width`` and ``height``.

kw.name: Capture Page Screenshot
kw.doc: Takes a screenshot of the current page and embeds it into a log file.

kw.name: Click Element
kw.doc: Click the element identified by ``locator``.

kw.name: Close Browser
kw.doc: Closes the current browser.
